<div class="hero-unit">
  <p><h1>Understanding Code Metrics</h1></p>

  <p>This is Mezuro! A <strong>free/libre</strong> web platform for <strong>collaborative</strong> source code <strong>evaluation</strong>.</p>

  <p>Here you can evaluate your source code with the most popular SCMs (Git SVN), just by providing it's URL. For now, you can evaluate <strong>C</strong>, <strong>C++</strong>, and <strong>Java</strong> source codes, but soon we hope to support more languages!</p>

  <p> Mezuro is under development. Try it and give us your <%= link_to 'feedback', 'https://github.com/mezuro/mezuro/issues', target: '_blank' %>.</p>
</div>

